        img(src='/static/imgs/pc/security/security_grid2.jpg', alt='P2P网贷平台').grid2-img
    .i-mod-warp.i-security-write
      .i-security-item
        .font-xxll.padding-xl
          span.weight 合作机构
          |&nbsp— 严格筛选与管理
        .security-item-two.clearfix.br-b-d2
          .span6.font-s.tl.people-text
            .weight.font-l 合作机构筛选：
            p
              span.weight 选择：
              |权威评级前3%、具有担保资质的优秀机构
