              |结合权威评级、资产规模、往期案例表现，综合评定、并给合作机构相应的授信额度
            p
              span.weight 实时监控：
              |实时监控合作机构资产情况
          .span6
            img(src='/static/imgs/pc/security/security_people.jpg', alt='p2p金融')
        .security-item-two.clearfix.br-b-d2
          .span6
            img(src='/static/imgs/pc/security/security_write.jpg', alt='p2p金融').write-img
          .span6.tl.font-s
            .weight.font-l.gm-t-l 合作机构对借款企业一级审核：
            p
              span.weight 实地考察：
              |实地考察借款人
            p
              span.weight 背景调查：
